        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Will my Germantown website rank in Google's Local Pack?",
          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Local Pack rankings depend on your Google Business Profile, review velocity, and local citations - not just your website. We handle the website side: LocalBusiness schema with correct Germantown NAP data, city-specific service pages targeting Damascus, Clarksburg, and Boyds, internal linking, and Core Web Vitals in the green. That's the foundation every Local Pack ranking in upcounty Montgomery County is built on." }
        },
