          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Do you build multilingual websites for Germantown's diverse business community?",
          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Germantown is one of the most linguistically diverse communities in Maryland, with large South Asian, Latin American, East Asian, and East African populations. We build multilingual WordPress sites using WPML with proper hreflang tags, supporting Spanish, Hindi, Korean, Amharic, and other languages your customers actually use. Multilingual SEO structures are built in from the start - not added as an afterthought - so each language version ranks independently in Google for Germantown searches." }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
});

